
This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you of how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information.

Information Collected
1.1 Information Collected Automatically
When you use our services, we may automatically collect certain information such as your IP address, device type, browser type, access time, and pages accessed.

1.2 Information You Provide
When you register an account, fill out forms, or interact with our services, we may ask you to provide personal information such as your name, email address, and contact number.

Use of Information
We may use the information collected to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our services
Respond to your inquiries and requests
Send service-related notifications, such as technical notices, security alerts, and support messages
Monitor and analyze the usage and trends of our services
Sharing and Disclosure of Information
We will not sell or otherwise share your personal information with third parties unless:

You give us permission
In order to comply with the law or respond to legal requests, such as subpoenas or court orders
We believe that disclosing information is necessary to protect our rights, property, or safety, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of users or the public
Third-Party Services
This service may contain links to other websites or services. Please note that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party websites or services.

Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from loss, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

Children’s Privacy
Our services are not aimed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.

Changes
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. We encourage you to regularly review this Privacy Policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at xsmuyu@gmail.com.

本隐私政策旨在告知您我们如何收集、使用和披露您的个人信息。

1. 收集的信息

1.1 自动收集的信息
当您使用我们的服务时，我们可能会自动收集某些信息，如您的IP地址、设备类型、浏览器类型、访问时间和访问页面。

1.2 提供的信息
当您注册账户、填写表格或与我们的服务互动时，我们可能会要求您提供个人信息，如姓名、电子邮件地址和联系电话。

2. 信息的使用

我们可能会使用收集的信息来：

提供、维护和改进我们的服务
响应您的咨询和请求
发送与服务相关的通知，如技术通知、安全警告和支持消息
监控和分析服务的使用和趋势
3. 信息的共享和披露

我们不会出售或以其他方式分享您的个人信息给第三方，除非：

您给予我们许可
为了遵守法律或响应法律请求，如传票或法院命令
我们认为披露信息是为了保护我们的权利、财产或安全，或保护用户或公众的权利、财产或安全所必需的
4. 第三方服务

本服务可能包含指向其他网站或服务的链接。请注意，我们不对这些第三方网站或服务的隐私做法负责。

5. 安全

我们采取合理的措施来保护您的个人信息免受丢失、滥用、未经授权的访问、披露、更改或破坏。

6. 儿童的隐私

我们的服务不针对13岁以下的儿童。我们不会故意收集13岁以下儿童的个人信息。

7. 更改

我们保留随时修改本隐私政策的权利。任何更改将在本页面发布，并带有更新日期。我们鼓励您定期查看本隐私政策。

8. 联系我们

如果您对本隐私政策有任何问题或疑虑，请通过xsmuyu@gmail.com与我们联系。

